000100 IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
000200 PROGRAM-ID. ARITHMETIC.
000300*
000400 DATA DIVISION.
000500 WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
000600 01  WS-A            PIC 9(5) VALUE ZEROS.
000700 01  WS-B            PIC 9(5) VALUE ZEROS.
000800 01  WS-RESULT       PIC 9(5) VALUE ZEROS.
000900*
001000 PROCEDURE DIVISION.
001100     MOVE 100 TO WS-A.
001200     MOVE 50 TO WS-B.
001300     ADD WS-A TO WS-B GIVING WS-RESULT.
001400     DISPLAY "ADD RESULT: " WS-RESULT.
001500     SUBTRACT WS-B FROM WS-A GIVING WS-RESULT.
001600     DISPLAY "SUBTRACT RESULT: " WS-RESULT.
001700     MULTIPLY WS-A BY WS-B GIVING WS-RESULT.
001800     DISPLAY "MULTIPLY RESULT: " WS-RESULT.
001900     DIVIDE WS-A BY WS-B GIVING WS-RESULT.
002000     DISPLAY "DIVIDE RESULT: " WS-RESULT.
